 <div class=\"col-md-12\">\r\n\r\n          <div class=\"halff-l-container half-fix\">\r\n          <section class=\"mgs-ux-r p-r-lg\">\r\n            <header>\r\n              <h2 class=\"m-b-lg servicios-h2\">\r\n                Custom applications \r\n              </h2>\r\n            </header>\r\n            <p class=\"gray-light-text lead ux-desc m-t-n-sm\">Web applications contribute to automate business processes, which lead to efficiency and productivity. We support you through the design process, development and digital application implementation. Our specialty is to make more with less, in a easy and intuitive way.  </p>\r\n            <div class=\"line25\"></div>\r\n          </section>\r\n        </div>\r\n      </div>\r\n    </div>\r\n   \r\n  </div>\r\n</div>\r\n\r\n<div class=\"full-width\">\r\n  <div class=\"row-height\">\r\n    <div class=\"col-sm-6 col-sm-height col-sm-middle p-none half-img-bg productivity-bg-img-2\"></div>\r\n    <div class=\"col-sm-6 col-sm-height col-sm-top p-none half-p-t-container bg-gray-light\">\r\n      <div class=\"col-md-12\">\r\n        <div class=\"halff-r-container half-fix refix\">\r\n          <section class=\"mgs-ux-l p-l-lg\">\r\n            <header>\r\n              <h2 class=\"m-b-lg servicios-h2\">\r\n                Data Analysis and visualization\r\n              </h2>\r\n            </header>\r\n            <p class=\"gray-light-text lead ux-desc m-t-n-sm\">Information is power. Any technology delivers data that are measurable and quantifiable as long as adequate tools are used, and offers a visual and intuitive overview. We support organizations in their data processing, report generation and intelligent visualization. Strategic decision-making and  continuous quality improvement process are some of the many tangible results for organizations.</p>\r\n            <div class=\"line25\"></div>\r\n          </section>\r\n        </div><!-- /half-container -->\r\n      </div>\r\n    </div>\r\n  </div>\r\n</div>