INSERT INTO `wp_posts` VALUES("245", "1", "2016-04-11 12:31:23", "2016-04-11 18:31:23", "<div class=\"jumbotron jumbotron-top vbt-bg jumbo-about\">\r\n  <div class=\"container\">\r\n    <h1 class=\"white-text m-b-none\">Virtual Bullet Time</h1>\r\n    <h2 class=\"m-t-n-xs\">\r\n      <small class=\"white-text\">4D mobile simulation and learning</small>\r\n    </h2>\r\n  </div>\r\n</div>\r\n\r\n<div id=\"trigger\" class=\"spacer s0 trigger-about\"></div>\r\n\r\n<div class=\"full-width\">\r\n  <div class=\"row-height\">\r\n    <div class=\"col-sm-6 col-sm-height col-sm-top p-none half-p-t-container bg-gray-light\">\r\n      <div class=\"roow\">\r\n        <div class=\"col-md-12\">\r\n\r\n          <div class=\"halff-l-container half-fix\">\r\n          <section class=\"mgs-ux-r p-r-lg\">\r\n            <header>\r\n              <h2 class=\"m-b-lg about-h2\">\r\n                The origin\r\n              </h2>\r\n            </header>\r\n            <p class=\"gray-light-text lead ux-desc m-t-n-sm\"><b>Virtual Bullet Time</b> is a 3D simulation solution that lets us understand different  scenarios that change over time. It aims to help people understand - in an autodidact way - the environment where a process, equipment or event are placed, and their relation with their environment as well. b>VBT</b> is oriented to offer an immersive learning experience. </p>\r\n            <p><b>VBT</b> was created from analyzing learning-teaching process in a production line. It works under the  on-the-job scheme, where an expert performs  an action that later will be executed by a group of trainees. In practice, it is complicated to  understand and apply those concepts  when we talk about concrete actions in different scenarios; we started to work on a solution.</p>\r\n          </section>\r\n        </div>\r\n        </div><!-- /half-container -->\r\n      </div>\r\n    </div>\r\n    <div class=\"col-sm-6 col-sm-height col-sm-middle p-none half-img-bg vbt-bg-img-1 hidden-xs\"></div>\r\n  </div>\r\n</div>\r\n\r\n<div class=\"container m-t-md m-b-md\">\r\n  <div class=\"row\">\r\n    <div class=\"col-xs-12 col-xs-offset-0 col-sm-12 col-sm-offset-0 col-md-10 col-md-offset-1 col-lg-8 col-lg-offset-2\">\r\n      <section>\r\n        <header>\r\n          <h3 class=\"m-b-lg\">\r\n            The solution\r\n          </h3>\r\n        </header>\r\n        <p>The acronym  <b>VBT</b> refers to the Bullet Time in movies industry ( a scene seems to be frozen in time and the camera runs through that frozen scene) Metagraphos has developed a solution that works similar to a camera visor but with one big difference: it can control multidimensional space.</p>\r\n\r\n        <div class=\"col-xs-12 col-xs-offset-0 col-sm-12 col-sm-offset-0 col-md-10 col-md-offset-1 col-lg-8 col-lg-offset-2\">\r\n          <blockquote class=\"text-md text-left quote\">\r\n            <p class=\"blockquote-text\">The development of Virtual Bullet Time  was a creative process inspired in cinema which allows us to convert practical learning - as we see in production line or oil platforms- in learning through virtual simulations. We take the best of science fiction to apply to more innovative learning - teaching processes, breaking grounds and proposing out-of-the-ordinary knowledge scenarios.</p>\r\n            <small class=\"text-right\">Ernesto Riestra, I+D  Metagraphos’s Director</small>\r\n          </blockquote>\r\n        </div>\r\n\r\n      </section>\r\n    </div>\r\n  </div>\r\n</div>\r\n\r\n<div class=\"container other-services \">\r\n  <!-- row of columns -->\r\n  <div class=\"row\">\r\n    <div class=\"col-sm-12\">\r\n      <section>\r\n        <div class=\"team\">\r\n          <div class=\"member-container col-sm-6 p-none\">\r\n            <figure class=\"member\">\r\n              <img class=\"img-responsive full-width\" src=\"http://localhost:8888/mgs-blog/wp-content/uploads/2016/04/vbt_img_2.jpg\"\r\n                   alt=\"\" />\r\n              <figcaption class=\"white-text\">\r\n              </figcaption>\r\n            </figure>\r\n          </div>\r\n          <div class=\"member-container col-sm-6 p-none\">\r\n            <figure class=\"member\">\r\n              <img class=\"img-responsive full-width hidden-xs\" src=\"http://localhost:8888/mgs-blog/wp-content/uploads/2016/04/vbt_img_3.jpg\"\r\n                   alt=\"\" />\r\n              <figcaption class=\"white-text\">\r\n              </figcaption>\r\n            </figure>\r\n          </div>\r\n        </div>\r\n      </section>\r\n    </div>\r\n  </div>\r\n</div> <!-- /container -->\r\n\r\n<div class=\"container methodology ben\">\r\n  <!-- row of columns -->\r\n  <div class=\"row\">\r\n    <div class=\"col-sm-12\">\r\n      <section>\r\n        <header>\r\n          <h3 class=\"Medium500 m-b-lg\">Benefits and distinctiveness</h3>\r\n        </header>\r\n        <div class=\"row\">\r\n          <div class=\"method-container col-sm-6 col-md-4\">\r\n            <article>\r\n              <p class=\"lead m-t-sm Normal400\">Our solution was born aiming to break learning-teaching lineal scheme processes . VTB simulates knowledge scenarios to change the trainee point of view, creating a simulated environment  through animations and step sequences that change along time. The user can place him/herself in any place and see anything, as it happens in a 3D movie.</p>\r\n              <h4 class=\"\">State-of-the- art-Technology</h4>\r\n              <p class=\"lead m-t-sm Normal400\"><b>VBT</b> is developed over the most advanced 3D simulation technologies, animation and interaction of the video game industry.  It was designed for mobile platforms to make the most of the interaction between the gyroscope and touch gestures, but it also can be deployed in standalone version for desktop devices or laptops. </p>\r\n            </article>\r\n          </div>\r\n          <div class=\"member-container col-sm-6 col-md-4\">\r\n            <article>\r\n              <h4 class=\"\">For everyone who looks to learn differently </h4>\r\n              <p class=\"lead m-t-sm Normal400\"><b>VBT</b> is designed for people who look for immersive learning experiences; for not only those who have a hard time leaving work to train in a classroom, but also for those who look for learning in a different way in real scenarios.</p>\r\n              <p class=\"lead m-t-sm Normal400\"><b>VBT</b> can be used to explain step-by-step when assembling household goods or furniture, to show the functioning sequence of a gearbox, or for a petroleum engineer to get used to the equipment in an oil platform.</p>\r\n              <h4 class=\"\">VBT future</h4>\r\n              <p class=\"lead m-t-sm Normal400\">The next version of Virtual Bullet Time will be integrated with virtual reality visor Oculus Rift and with Leap Motion. The creation of learning scenarios will be more attached to reality.</p>\r\n            </article>\r\n          </div>\r\n\r\n          <div class=\"member-container col-sm-6 col-md-4 fnone\">\r\n            <article>\r\n              <h4 class=\"\">Technology</h4>\r\n              <p class=\"gray-light-text\">Unity, WebGL</p>\r\n              <hr>\r\n\r\n              <h4 class=\"\">Contact</h4>\r\n              <p class=\"gray-light-text\">If you are interested in using <b>VBT</b> in your company, contact us: <a href=\"mailto:hola@metagraphos.com\">hola@metagraphos.com</a></p>\r\n              <hr>\r\n\r\n              <h4 class=\"\">For more information about VBT, see</h4>\r\n              <svg fill=\"#262520\" height=\"20\" viewBox=\"0 0 20 20\" width=\"20\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\">\r\n                    <path d=\"M0 0h24v24H0z\" fill=\"none\"/>\r\n                    <path d=\"M12 4l-1.41 1.41L16.17 11H4v2h12.17l-5.58 5.59L12 20l8-8z\"/>\r\n                </svg> \r\n              <a href=\"http://vbt.metagraphos.com\" target=\"_blank\" class=\"nlink\">\r\n                 vbt.metagraphos.com\r\n              </a>\r\n              <hr>\r\n\r\n              <h4 class=\"\">For more information about <b>VBT</b> download the app </h4>\r\n              <svg fill=\"#262520\" height=\"20\" viewBox=\"0 0 20 20\" width=\"20\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\">\r\n                    <path d=\"M0 0h24v24H0z\" fill=\"none\"/>\r\n                    <path d=\"M12 4l-1.41 1.41L16.17 11H4v2h12.17l-5.58 5.59L12 20l8-8z\"/>\r\n                </svg> \r\n              <a href=\"https://itunes.apple.com/us/app/vbt/id483971720?ls=1&mt=8\" target=\"_blank\" class=\"nlink\">\r\n                 App Store\r\n              </a>\r\n            </article>\r\n          </div>\r\n\r\n        </div>\r\n      </section>\r\n    </div>\r\n  </div>\r\n</div>\r\n\r\n<div class=\"pull-left image-roller\">\r\n  <div class=\"col-sm-6 p-none\">\r\n    <div class=\"col-sm-12 p-none\">\r\n      <img class=\"img-responsive full-width hidden-xs\" src=\"http://localhost:8888/mgs-blog/wp-content/uploads/2016/04/vbt_img_4.jpg\" alt=\"Metagraphos\" />\r\n    </div>\r\n    <div class=\"col-sm-12 p-none\">\r\n      <img class=\"img-responsive full-width\" src=\"http://localhost:8888/mgs-blog/wp-content/uploads/2016/04/vbt_img_5.jpg\" alt=\"Metagraphos\" />\r\n    </div>\r\n  </div>\r\n  <div class=\"col-sm-6 p-none\">\r\n    <img class=\"img-responsive full-width hidden-xs\" src=\"http://localhost:8888/mgs-blog/wp-content/uploads/2016/04/vbt_img_6.jpg\" alt=\"Metagraphos\" />\r\n  </div>\r\n</div>\r\n\r\n<div class=\"container other-services\">\r\n  <!-- row of columns -->\r\n  <div class=\"row\">\r\n    <div class=\"col-sm-12\">\r\n      <section>\r\n        <header>\r\n          <h3 class=\"Medium500 m-b-lg p-t-md\">Other products</h3>\r\n        </header>\r\n        <div class=\"team otros-productos\">\r\n          <div class=\"member-container figure-overlay col-sm-6 p-none\">\r\n            <a href=\"porta3d-en\">\r\n            <figure class=\"member\">\r\n              <img class=\"img-responsive full-width\" src=\"http://localhost:8888/mgs-blog/wp-content/uploads/2016/04/colormaze_img_7.jpg\"\r\n                   alt=\"Adriana Caballero CEO / Fundadora\" />\r\n\r\n              <figcaption class=\"white-text b-l\">\r\n                <p class=\"medium light300 titulo\">Five variables, only one graph</p>\r\n                <p class=\"text-xl m-b-n-sm descripcion\">Porta3D</p>\r\n              </figcaption>\r\n\r\n              <blockquote class=\"no-quotes light300 medium p-md\">\r\n                <svg fill=\"#ffffff\" height=\"20\" viewBox=\"0 0 20 20\" width=\"20\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\">\r\n                    <path d=\"M0 0h24v24H0z\" fill=\"none\"/>\r\n                    <path d=\"M12 4l-1.41 1.41L16.17 11H4v2h12.17l-5.58 5.59L12 20l8-8z\"/>\r\n                </svg>\r\n                <span>View information</span>\r\n            </figure>\r\n            </a>\r\n          </div>\r\n\r\n          <div class=\"member-container figure-overlay col-sm-6 p-none\">\r\n            <a href=\"colormaze-en\">\r\n            <figure class=\"member\">\r\n              <img class=\"img-responsive full-width\" src=\"http://localhost:8888/mgs-blog/wp-content/uploads/2016/04/fm-color-maze.jpg\"\r\n                   alt=\"Ernesto Riestra CTO / Fundadora\" />\r\n              <figcaption class=\"white-text b-l\">\r\n                <p class=\"medium light300 titulo\">3D Maze... with one spin!</p>\r\n                <p class=\"text-xl m-b-n-sm descripcion\">ColorMaze 3D</p>\r\n              </figcaption>\r\n\r\n              <blockquote class=\"no-quotes light300 medium p-md\">\r\n                <svg fill=\"#ffffff\" height=\"20\" viewBox=\"0 0 20 20\" width=\"20\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\">\r\n                    <path d=\"M0 0h24v24H0z\" fill=\"none\"/>\r\n                    <path d=\"M12 4l-1.41 1.41L16.17 11H4v2h12.17l-5.58 5.59L12 20l8-8z\"/>\r\n                </svg>\r\n                <span>View information</span>\r\n            </figure>\r\n            </a>\r\n          </div>\r\n        </div>\r\n      </section>\r\n    </div>\r\n  </div>\r\n</div> <!-- /container -->", "Virtual Bullet Time", "", "inherit", "closed", "closed", "", "237-revision-v1", "", "", "2016-04-11 12:31:23", "2016-04-11 18:31:23", "", "237", "http://localhost:8888/mgs-blog/237-revision-v1/", "0", "revision", "", "0");
INSERT INTO `wp_posts` VALUES("246", "1", "2016-04-11 12:37:26", "2016-04-11 18:37:26", "<!-- Main jumbotron for a primary marketing message or call to action -->\r\n<div class=\"jumbotron jumbotron-top colormaze-bg jumbo-about\">\r\n  <div class=\"container\">\r\n    <h1 class=\"white-text m-b-none\">ColorMaze</h1>\r\n    <h2 class=\"m-t-n-xs\">\r\n      <small class=\"white-text\">3D Maze... with one spin!</small>\r\n    </h2>\r\n  </div>\r\n</div>\r\n\r\n<div id=\"trigger\" class=\"spacer s0 triger-about\"></div>\r\n\r\n<div class=\"full-width\">\r\n  <div class=\"row-height\">\r\n    <div class=\"col-sm-6 col-sm-height col-sm-top p-none half-p-t-container bg-gray-light\">\r\n      <div class=\"roow\">\r\n        <div class=\"col-md-12\">\r\n\r\n          <div class=\"halff-l-container half-fix\">\r\n          <section class=\"mgs-ux-r p-r-lg\">\r\n            <header>\r\n              <h2 class=\"m-b-lg about-h2\">\r\n                The origin\r\n              </h2>\r\n            </header>\r\n            <p class=\"gray-light-text lead ux-desc m-t-n-sm\"><b>ColorMaze</b> emerged as an agile development experiment in a short time. It is a casual game that combines touch interactions , gyroscopes and accelerometers. The game aims to move a series of colored mini balls through a tridimensional maze to make them reach their same color target. Most of the levels are easy although some of them are quite challenging.  The maze rotates in accordance to the device’s  movements, but also can be rotated with touch gestures for those who don’t like to get dizzy. </p>\r\n          </section>\r\n        </div>\r\n        </div><!-- /half-container -->\r\n      </div>\r\n    </div>\r\n    <div class=\"col-sm-6 col-sm-height col-sm-middle p-none half-img-bg colormaze-bg-img-1 hidden-xs\"></div>\r\n  </div>\r\n</div>\r\n\r\n<div class=\"container m-t-md m-b-md\">\r\n  <div class=\"row\">\r\n    <div class=\"col-xs-12 col-xs-offset-0 col-sm-12 col-sm-offset-0 col-md-10 col-md-offset-1 col-lg-8 col-lg-offset-2\">\r\n      <section>\r\n        <header>\r\n          <h3 class=\"m-b-lg\">\r\n            The solution\r\n          </h3>\r\n        </header>\r\n        <p>In general, games that use gyroscopes produce a spin in a 1 to 1 relationship, making the user rotate in his/her axis and sometimes it is not possible if the user is sitting.</p>\r\n\r\n        <div class=\"col-xs-12 col-xs-offset-0 col-sm-12 col-sm-offset-0 col-md-10 col-md-offset-1 col-lg-8 col-lg-offset-2\">\r\n          <blockquote class=\"text-md text-left quote\">\r\n            <p class=\"blockquote-text\">When creating <b>ColorMaze</b>,  the most remarkable aspect we learned  was that even in a simple casual game we could discover interesting and exciting things.To develop  this game, we set ourselves a challenge to demonstrate that we not only know how to create applications for productivity and training but also for entertaining, which fits in our vision. </p>\r\n            <small class=\"text-right\">Ernesto Riestra, I+D  Metagraphos’s Director</small>\r\n          </blockquote>\r\n        </div>\r\n\r\n      </section>\r\n    </div>\r\n  </div>\r\n</div>\r\n\r\n<div class=\"container other-services \">\r\n  <!-- row of columns -->\r\n  <div class=\"row\">\r\n    <div class=\"col-sm-12\">\r\n      <section>\r\n        <div class=\"team\">\r\n\r\n          <div class=\"member-container col-sm-6 p-none\">\r\n            <figure class=\"member\">\r\n              <img class=\"img-responsive full-width\" src=\"http://localhost:8888/mgs-blog/wp-content/uploads/2016/04/colormaze_img_2.jpg\"\r\n                   alt=\"\" />\r\n              <figcaption class=\"white-text\">\r\n              </figcaption>\r\n            </figure>\r\n          </div>\r\n\r\n          <div class=\"member-container col-sm-6 p-none\">\r\n            <figure class=\"member\">\r\n              <img class=\"img-responsive full-width foot-hide\" src=\"http://localhost:8888/mgs-blog/wp-content/uploads/2016/04/colormaze_img_3.jpg\"\r\n                   alt=\"\" />\r\n              <figcaption class=\"white-text\">\r\n              </figcaption>\r\n            </figure>\r\n          </div>\r\n\r\n        </div>\r\n      </section>\r\n    </div>\r\n  </div>\r\n</div> <!-- /container -->\r\n\r\n<div class=\"container methodology ben\">\r\n  <!-- row of columns -->\r\n  <div class=\"row\">\r\n    <div class=\"col-sm-12\">\r\n      <section>\r\n        <header>\r\n          <h3 class=\"Medium500 m-b-lg\">Distinctiveness</h3>\r\n        </header>\r\n        <div class=\"row\">\r\n          <div class=\"method-container col-sm-6 col-md-4\">\r\n            <article>\r\n              <p class=\"lead m-t-sm Normal400\"><b>ColorMaze</b> uses an interesting principle regarding space orientation, offering the user to go further. The rotation model takes the device’s orientation and then multiplies it by an additional factor, allowing big spins with a slight rotation. We added a friendly interface design to this project as well as user experience (UX) to use an adequate tridimensional space according to touch and gyroscope features. This makes <b>ColorMaze</b> a self-explanatory game.  </p>\r\n              <p class=\"lead m-t-sm Normal400\">For those who are interested in math, the rotation in space can be modeled in at least three ways, the first are exponential functions, the second, rotation matrixes and the third, quaternions. </p>\r\n              <p class=\"lead m-t-sm Normal400\">These have very interesting attributes since they do not present any kind of “singularity”, which is an uncomfortable effect in video games when turning to see in vertical direction, especially in type FPS (First Person Shooter) games. </p>\r\n            </article>\r\n          </div>\r\n          <div class=\"member-container col-sm-6 col-md-4\">\r\n            <article>\r\n              <p class=\"lead m-t-sm Normal400\">In other words, <b>ColorMaze</b> implements a “quaternion acceleration”  which is an amusing way to refer to an improved interaction. </p>\r\n              <h4 class=\"\">Technology</h4>\r\n              <p class=\"lead m-t-sm Normal400\">This acceleration also allows an interesting effect: when the player moves his device not only he changes his point of view but also modifies the maze’s orientation. This way, we have achieved not only an interactive 3D view but also integrate, in the same view, the player’s direct action.</p>\r\n              <p class=\"lead m-t-sm Normal400\">In addition, <b>ColorMaze</b> contains a gravity associated to the user’s system; it means that the gravity in real world and in the game are always aligned.</p>\r\n            </article>\r\n          </div>\r\n          <div class=\"member-container col-sm-6 col-md-4 fnone\">\r\n            <article>\r\n              <h4 class=\"\">Technology</h4>\r\n              <p class=\"gray-light-text\">Unity, WebGL</p>\r\n              <hr>\r\n\r\n              <h4 class=\"\">Download ColorMaze</h4>\r\n              <p class=\"gray-light-text\">Ir a la <a href=\"https://itunes.apple.com/us/app/colormaze-3d/id880855990?mt=8\" target=\"_blank\">App Store</a></p>\r\n            </article>\r\n          </div>\r\n        </div>\r\n      </section>\r\n    </div>\r\n  </div>\r\n</div>\r\n\r\n<!--<div class=\"pull-left\">\r\n  <div class=\"col-sm-6 p-none\">\r\n    <div class=\"col-sm-12 p-none\">\r\n      <img class=\"img-responsive full-width\" src=\"http://localhost:8888/mgs-blog/wp-content/uploads/2016/04/colormaze_img_4.jpg\" alt=\"Metagraphos\" />\r\n    </div>\r\n    <div class=\"col-sm-12 p-none\">\r\n      <img class=\"img-responsive full-width\" src=\"http://localhost:8888/mgs-blog/wp-content/uploads/2016/04/colormaze_img_5.jpg\" alt=\"Metagraphos\" />\r\n    </div>\r\n  </div>\r\n  <div class=\"col-sm-6 p-none\">\r\n    <img class=\"img-responsive full-width\" src=\"http://localhost:8888/mgs-blog/wp-content/uploads/2016/04/colormaze_img_6.jpg\" alt=\"Metagraphos