 to construct an innovative proposal regarding productivity and knowledge that sustain their strategic areas <em>- IT, sales, human resources and marketing - </em> in reaching their objectives in a efficient and friendly way.</p>\r\n        </div>\r\n        <div class=\"col-sm-6 desc\">\r\n          <p class=\"lead ux-desc m-t-n-sm\">In <b>metagraphos</b>, we innovate to transform your company  knowledge, productivity and technology  through friendly and intuitive  digital experiences. We combine design thinking, innovation and knowledge to bring your company to the digital era.</p>\r\n        </div>\r\n      </div>\r\n    </section>\r\n  </div>\r\n</div>\r\n\r\n<div class=\"container\">\r\n  <div class=\"col-sm-12 p-none\">\r\n    <img class=\"img-responsive full-width\" src=\"http://localhost:8888/mgs-blog/wp-content/uploads/2016/04/corporate_img_2.jpg\" alt=\"\" />\r\n  </div>\r\n</div>\r\n\r\n<div class=\"container other-services otros-sectores\">\r\n  <!-- row of columns -->\r\n  <div class=\"row\">\r\n    <div class=\"col-sm-12\">\r\n      <section>\r\n        <header>\r\n          <h3 class=\"Medium500 m-b-lg enfoque-tit\">Sectors</h3>\r\n        </header>\r\n        <div class=\"team\">\r\n          <div class=\"member-container figure-overlay col-sm-6 p-none\">\r\n            <a href=\"government\">\r\n            <figure class=\"member\">\r\n              <img class=\"img-responsive full-width\" src=\"http://localhost:8888/mgs-blog/wp-content/uploads/2016/04/fm-gobierno.jpg\"\r\n                   alt=\"Adriana Caballero CEO / Fundadora\" />\r\n              \r\n              <figcaption class=\"white-text b-l\">\r\n<!--                     <p class=\"medium light300 titulo\">Cinco variables una soloa gráfica</p>\r\n-->                    <p class=\"text-xl m-b-n-sm descripcion\">Government</p>\r\n              </figcaption>\r\n\r\n              <blockquote class=\"no-quotes light300 medium p-md\">\r\n                <svg fill=\"#ffffff\" height=\"20\" vi